About this item

  • Made with 100% human-grade ingredients like chicken, eggs, fresh-freeze dried vegetables, organic spices, and vitamins & minerals, that offers holistic nutrition in every meal
  • Artisanal batches baked at a low heat temperature to preserve natural ingredients

Product Description

Make a Healthy Change for Your Pet's Well-being - Switch to Henlo!

Henlo's dedication to pet parents stems from a shared concern for inadequate information and quality in pet food. This worry inspired a revolutionary recipe, reshaping the pet nutrition landscape. Henlo addresses the concerns of all pet parents with premium ingredients, a unique low-heat baking process, and a vet-approved formula. This commitment echoes the sentiments of every caring pet parent, ensuring Henlo transcends dog food; it's a testament to love, quality, and holistic pet well-being.

Protein Powerhouse

Henlo's high-protein formula nurtures muscle development and overall well-being in your pet, ensuring robust health and vitality.

Lustrous Coat

Henlo fosters optimal coat health for your beloved pet, ensuring a soft and radiant coat that reflects their inner vitality.

Gentle and Easy Digestion

Henlo's easily digestible recipe is crafted for gentle digestion, ensuring a comfortable mealtime experience for your pet.

100% Human grade ingredients

Henlo uses only the highest quality, 100% human-grade ingredients that ensures a wholesome and nutrient rich balanced diet.

Henlo's Irresistible Taste, Crafted with Premium Ingredients

Indulge your pet with an exceptional blend of premium ingredients, featuring fresh whole eggs, human grade chicken, and a medley of vibrant freeze-dried veggies including Carrot, Pumpkin, Beetroot, Sweet Potato, and Green Beans. Our commitment to quality extends to the addition of Cinnamon and anti-inflammatory Ginger Powder, ensuring a delicious meal, free from artificial additives and by-products. Henlo, where every ingredient is selected with care for your pet's health and happiness.

Start with a taste of Henlo!

Days 1-3: Start the flavor journey by Mixing 1/4th of Henlo with 3/4th of the current dry food for a tasty transition!

Balancing Act of 50/50

Days 4-5: Create harmony in every bite by mixing equal parts Henlo and your dog's current dry food for a delightful adaptation.

Elevate the Taste Journey

Days 6-7: Let your dog get cozy with Henlo and shift to 3/4th Henlo and 1/4th current dry food for a smoother, flavor-packed transition.

Embrace the full flavor!

Day 8: Make the switch to 100% Henlo Baked Dry Dog Food for a feast of complete nutrition and full-on Henlo happiness!

Henlo's Uniqueness: Know What Makes it Special

  • Trusted by Veterinarians
  • No Artificial Additives
  • Premium 100% Human Grade Chicken
  • Artisanal Baking at Low Heat
  • Human-Friendly Aroma

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Deborah of Bible
1.0 out of 5 stars Not recommended puppy food
Reviewed in India on 1 November 2023
Size: 6 kg (Pack of 1)Style Name: PuppyVerified Purchase
Let me get to points on why I have rated HENLO puppy food 1 star.
1. The kibbles are too big for a puppy (especially 3-6 months).
2. It does not get digested even in the 6 hours of the time a puppy takes to digest the proteins.
3. My puppy threw up the Henlo in 5 hours and the vet form supertails asked me to immediately stop Henlo. Point to notice here is that super tails recommends the gms of this food to give your pup based on the wt.
4. The kibbles are too hard and I'm not sure if the the same is slow baked to make the chicken so hard and dry unless and until it has carbs that is not right for a puppy as the same is not easily digested.
5. No published data available in what they claim in videos and product description. I emailed twice for them to share the data every food company is supposed to make public and the certifications they have got, including the claimed nutritional values, and they everted only after weeks post an honest review was made.
6. Henlo's 1800 number is not reachable so point 5 and 6 indicates, they do not have anyone to answer customer queries.
7. I noticed my pup's growth slowed. She is 4 months now and we know that this is the peak of growth.
8. This dry food is not at all suitable even for adults dogs especially with intolerant stomachs like GSDs as it is slow to digest meaning takes more than the 6 hours of protein digest time taken and can develop gastro problems. For a puppy who is fed 3-4 times a day this is a big no no.
9. Why must you not give the names of the chef/vet/dietician who created this food. Point is there is no information that verifies claims made for this puppy food.
10. Being a pet parent who is concerned on the good health and longevity of my pet, I am not moving ahead with Henlo in the near future.
11. LATER Henlo resolved the issue, showing they do care for the pets and pet parents and hope there are improvements made for sensitive puppy stomachs and trail data is published. Wish them best in the near future!
